        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51685",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ralf",
                        "name": "ralf",
                        "displayName": "Ralf Eggert",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I add this here, since it is somehow connected. When I add a submit button to a form, the value attribute holds the text displayed on the button. Unfortunately, this value text is not translated at all. Zend\\Form\\View\\Helper\\FormSubmit needs to be change to get the value translated if a translator object is set. FormReset and FormButton have the same problem.\r\n\r\nEither FormInput::render() must be changed for this or FormSubmit, FormReset and FormButton need to have their own render() method for translation the value attribute.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=ralf",
                        "name": "ralf",
                        "displayName": "Ralf Eggert",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-23T20:33:06.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-23T20:33:06.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51687",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Ralf -- I think that particular instance is fixed on current master due to a PR I merged earlier today. Can you please test?",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=matthew",
                        "name": "matthew",
                        "displayName": "Matthew Weier O'Phinney",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-23T21:11:25.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2012-08-23T21:11:25.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/51688",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=cgmartin",
                        "name": "cgmartin",
                        "displayName": "Chris Martin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Matthew - The earlier PR I think only addressed FormButton. FormSubmit and FormReset are currently still outstanding.\r\n\r\nI have a PR ready for FormSubmit (marked for 2.1): https:\/\/github.com\/zendframework\/zf2\/pull\/2124\r\n...but FormReset would need the same logic. I will update FormReset and commit to this same PR.\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=cgmartin",
                        "name": "cgmartin",
                        "displayName": "Chris Martin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2012-08-23T21:20:00.000+0000",
